intent.user_query: Which product categories have the lowest customer satisfaction based on service feedback?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(s.ServiceRating) AS AverageSatisfaction FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceRequests sr ON p.ProductID = sr.ProductID JOIN fitness_db.ServiceFeedback s ON sr.ServiceRequestID = s.ServiceRequestID GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY AverageSatisfaction ASC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(s.ServiceRating) AS AverageSatisfaction FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.ServiceRequests sr ON p.ProductID = sr.ProductID JOIN fitness_db.ServiceFeedback s ON sr.ServiceRequestID = s.ServiceRequestID GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY AverageSatisfaction ASC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
